        <title>Virtuozzo Storage driver</title>
        <paragraph>The Virtuozzo Storage driver is a fault-tolerant distributed storage
            system that is optimized for virtualization workloads.
            Set the following in your <literal>cinder.conf</literal> file, and use the following
            options to configure it.</paragraph>
